{"tid":2196670,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"參加動漫祭露下體給人拍 女大生遭起訴","createTime":"2020-09-10T05:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T06:48:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f38496ac1910a81b2e732b3b98dfad8a7484912c","tid":2196670,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"一名休學中的台灣科技大學的李姓女大生，今年7月4日到台北市花博公園爭豔館參加動漫祭，卻在戶外掀開裙子，露出沒穿內褲的下體供人拍攝，台北地檢署考量李女涉公然猥褻的罪證明確，今天將她起訴。<br />\n<br />\n檢警調查，李女自行參加動漫祭，而非收到主辦單位邀請，她當天穿著水手服、戴假髮，在主辦場地上自行用手掀開裙子，露出沒穿內褲的下體讓人拍攝。不少到場參加活動的人見到，有人拍照存證，也有人向主辦單位反映。<br />\n<br />\n台科大則在事發後對外致歉，表示李女因身心問題，已休學1年半，後續將提供心理諮商。<br />\n<br />\n事後李女則發文，駁斥網傳她神隱說法，指出是手機有問題，也說已和校方聯繫上，朋友不必擔心，最後不忘嗆「歡迎在台北街頭捕捉野生的我」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/society/breakingnews/3287267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287267&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=19376078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287267&h=4470f2fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/society/breakingnews/3287267</a>"},{"pid":"00caa7dc16465c64d066d72b3228bca1e4e187a4","tid":2196670,"uid":127905,"like":291,"dislike":12,"score":279,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"人地露個閪出黎俾我地睇係應該心存感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲仆街搞到我地以後冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be74b487f2d0f3d2e5fcac466f06ba8b41e4c49e","tid":2196670,"uid":123926,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"留名等無格版"},{"pid":"cf794ee548e41d743d39c8bc02b9466fc46a3d63","tid":2196670,"uid":207710,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"女權撚去咗邊"},{"pid":"70a79949a2ceda1e29d3bc1432be